---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="ZERO OS — Trading Intelligence Infrastructure">

<div class="page">

  <!-- CRT BOOT -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="boot-sequence">
      <pre class="boot-line b1"><span class="p">ZERO OS</span> v0.1 .................... <span class="p">BOOT</span></pre>
      <pre class="boot-line b2"><span class="p">ENVY MATRIX</span> .................... <span class="p">5 CHAOS INDICATORS</span></pre>
      <pre class="boot-line b3"><span class="p">REGIME DETECTION</span> ............... <span class="p">ONLINE</span></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <pre class="logo-art">████████╗ ███████╗ ██████╗   ██████╗
╚══███╔═╝ ██╔════╝ ██╔══██╗ ██╔═══██╗
  ███╔╝   █████╗   ██████╔╝ ██║   ██║
 ███╔╝    ██╔══╝   ██╔══██╗ ██║   ██║
████████╗ ███████╗ ██║  ██║ ╚██████╔╝
╚═══════╝ ╚══════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝  ╚═════╝</pre>
      <div class="crt-scanline"></div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="hero-title">AI that trades better than you.<br>And you're okay with it.</h1>

    <p class="hero-sub">
      Chaos mathematics applied to crypto markets. Hurst exponents, DFA, Lyapunov — 
      indicators that tell you which regime you're in before your strategy fails.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#access" class="btn-primary">Request Early Access</a>
      <a href="#signals" class="btn-ghost">See it live ↓</a>
      <a href="/thesis" class="btn-ghost">Read the thesis</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- LIVE SIGNAL MATRIX -->
  <section class="section" id="signals">
    <div class="matrix-head">
      <p class="section-label p">SIGNAL MATRIX — LIVE</p>
      <span class="matrix-status" id="matrix-status">scanning</span>
    </div>
    <div class="matrix-wrap">
      <canvas id="matrix-canvas"></canvas>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE EDGE + POSITIONING (merged) -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label p reveal-child">THE EDGE</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal-child">Traditional indicators assume one regime. Markets have many.</h2>

    <div class="edge-contrast reveal-child">
      <div class="edge-row">
        <span class="edge-them dim">RSI says overbought</span>
        <span class="edge-us p">We know if RSI even applies in this regime</span>
      </div>
      <div class="edge-row">
        <span class="edge-them dim">MACD shows a crossover</span>
        <span class="edge-us p">We tell you if that crossover is meaningful or a trap ↓</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="regime-viz reveal-child">
      <div class="rv-bar-group">
        <div class="rv-bar">
          <span class="rv-label dim">HURST</span>
          <div class="rv-track">
            <div class="rv-fill" id="rv-hurst"></div>
            <div class="rv-marker" id="rv-hurst-marker"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="rv-val" id="rv-hurst-val">0.50</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rv-bar">
          <span class="rv-label dim">DFA</span>
          <div class="rv-track">
            <div class="rv-fill" id="rv-dfa"></div>
            <div class="rv-marker" id="rv-dfa-marker"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="rv-val" id="rv-dfa-val">0.50</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rv-bar">
          <span class="rv-label dim">LYAPUNOV</span>
          <div class="rv-track">
            <div class="rv-fill rv-fill-lyap" id="rv-lyap"></div>
            <div class="rv-marker" id="rv-lyap-marker"></div>
          </div>
          <span class="rv-val" id="rv-lyap-val">0.00</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rv-output">
        <div class="rv-regime-badge" id="rv-badge">SCANNING</div>
        <p class="rv-verdict" id="rv-verdict">Your MACD crossover is → <span class="p">ANALYZING</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROPOSAL F: LIVING DISCOVERY CARDS -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label a reveal-child">EMERGENT SIGNALS</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal-child">The system discovered these. We didn't program them.</h2>
    <div class="discovery-grid reveal-child">
      <div class="disc-card tilt-card" data-accent="phosphor">
        <canvas class="disc-canvas" id="disc-hurst" width="200" height="60"></canvas>
        <div class="disc-val p" id="disc-hurst-val">H = 0.41</div>
        <p>Mean-reverting — reversal windows no human hypothesized</p>
      </div>
      <div class="disc-card tilt-card" data-accent="amber">
        <canvas class="disc-canvas" id="disc-winloss" width="200" height="60"></canvas>
        <div class="disc-val a" id="disc-hr-val">&lt;30% HR</div>
        <p>Low hit rate, massive payoff — the wins dominate</p>
      </div>
      <div class="disc-card tilt-card" data-accent="ice">
        <canvas class="disc-canvas" id="disc-sent" width="200" height="60"></canvas>
        <div class="disc-val ice">Δ SENT</div>
        <p>Analyst-crowd divergence — contrarian signal invisible to price</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROPOSAL G: TIMELINE TOWER + H: CIRCULAR FLYWHEEL -->
  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label p reveal-child">THREE LAYERS</p>

    <div class="timeline reveal-child">
      <!-- spine -->
      <div class="tl-spine"></div>

      <!-- L1 -->
      <div class="tl-node tl-l1 tilt-card">
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-p"></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3 class="layer-title"><span class="p">L1</span> Signal-as-a-Service <span class="layer-tag tag-live p">LIVE</span></h3>
          <p class="layer-desc dim">Raw alpha via API. Not indicators — discoveries. For funds and trading desks that have infrastructure but not this data edge.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- L2 -->
      <div class="tl-node tl-l2 tilt-card">
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-a"></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3 class="layer-title"><span class="a">L2</span> Agent Marketplace <span class="layer-tag tag-build a">BUILDING</span></h3>
          <p class="layer-desc dim">Engineers build predictors → agents find combinations → best agents attract capital → engineers earn revenue share.</p>
          <!-- Circular Flywheel SVG -->
          <div class="fw-circle-wrap">
            <svg class="fw-circle" viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="180" height="180">
              <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="75" fill="none" stroke="rgba(26,26,26,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <!-- nodes -->
              <g id="fw-nodes">
                <g class="fw-node" data-fw="0" transform="translate(100,25)">
                  <rect x="-28" y="-9" width="56" height="18" rx="2" fill="rgba(26,26,26,0.8)" stroke="rgba(138,130,120,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="0" y="4" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,228,223,0.7)" font-size="7" font-weight="700" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">Engineers</text>
                </g>
                <g class="fw-node" data-fw="1" transform="translate(171,62)">
                  <rect x="-30" y="-9" width="60" height="18" rx="2" fill="rgba(26,26,26,0.8)" stroke="rgba(138,130,120,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="0" y="4" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,228,223,0.7)" font-size="7" font-weight="700" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">Predictors</text>
                </g>
                <g class="fw-node" data-fw="2" transform="translate(147,150)">
                  <rect x="-22" y="-9" width="44" height="18" rx="2" fill="rgba(26,26,26,0.8)" stroke="rgba(138,130,120,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="0" y="4" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,228,223,0.7)" font-size="7" font-weight="700" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">Agents</text>
                </g>
                <g class="fw-node" data-fw="3" transform="translate(53,150)">
                  <rect x="-22" y="-9" width="44" height="18" rx="2" fill="rgba(26,26,26,0.8)" stroke="rgba(138,130,120,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="0" y="4" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,228,223,0.7)" font-size="7" font-weight="700" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">Capital</text>
                </g>
                <g class="fw-node" data-fw="4" transform="translate(29,62)">
                  <rect x="-26" y="-9" width="52" height="18" rx="2" fill="rgba(26,26,26,0.8)" stroke="rgba(138,130,120,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="0" y="4" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,228,223,0.7)" font-size="7" font-weight="700" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace">Revenue</text>
                </g>
              </g>
              <!-- rotating glow -->
              <circle id="fw-glow" cx="100" cy="25" r="6" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,255,0,0.5)" stroke-width="2">
                <animateMotion dur="4s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M100,25 A75,75 0 0,1 171,62 A75,75 0 0,1 147,150 A75,75 0 0,1 53,150 A75,75 0 0,1 29,62 A75,75 0 0,1 100,25"/>
              </circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- L3 -->
      <div class="tl-node tl-l3 tilt-card">
        <div class="tl-dot tl-dot-ice"></div>
        <div class="tl-content">
          <h3 class="layer-title"><span class="ice">L3</span> One-click execution <span class="layer-tag tag-vision ice">VISION</span></h3>
          <p class="layer-desc dim">14 months live PnL. Verified Sharpe. Documented drawdown. One button.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="vision-quote reveal-child">
      <span class="dim">»</span> The line between a trading system and a world model starts to blur. 
      That is the point we are building toward.
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- TERMINAL CTA (with status merged) -->
  <section class="section cta-section reveal" id="access">
    <div class="term-cta reveal-child">
      <div class="term-header">
        <span class="dim">zero-os</span>
        <span class="term-dots">
          <span class="dot dot-r"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-a"></span>
          <span class="dot dot-p"></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="term-body">
        <p class="term-line dim">$ zero-os --status</p>
        <p class="term-line"><span class="p">&gt;</span> Regime detection engine: <span class="p">BUILT</span></p>
        <p class="term-line"><span class="p">&gt;</span> Signal API: <span class="a">PRE-LAUNCH</span></p>
        <p class="term-line"><span class="p">&gt;</span> Seeking design partners — funds and desks who want first access.</p>
        <p class="term-line dim" style="margin-top:0.5rem">$ zero-os request_access</p>
        <form class="term-form" id="access-form" action="#" method="POST">
          <div class="term-input-row">
            <span class="p">email:</span>
            <input type="email" id="access-email" class="term-input" placeholder="you@fund.com" required autocomplete="email">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="term-submit">SUBMIT ↵</button>
        </form>
        <p class="term-confirm" id="term-confirm" style="display:none">
          <span class="p">✓ ACCESS_REQUEST_QUEUED</span><br>
          <span class="dim">ref: ZOS-<span id="req-id">0000</span> — we'll be in touch.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="term-error" id="term-error" style="display:none">
          <span class="red">✗ CONNECTION_ERROR</span><br>
          <span class="dim">Try again or email <a href="mailto:degenie@getzero.dev" style="color:var(--phosphor);">degenie@getzero.dev</a> directly.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer reveal">
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="https://x.com/squaer_agent" class="footer-link dim" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X ↗</a>
      <span class="footer-sep dim">·</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/squaeragent" class="footer-link dim" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
      <span class="footer-sep dim">·</span>
      <a href="mailto:degenie@getzero.dev" class="footer-link dim">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-copy dim">
      <span class="p">◇</span> ZERO OS — chaos-aware trading infrastructure
    </div>
  </footer>

</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
  }

  /* CRT */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 4px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 70% at 50% 50%, transparent 0%, transparent 85%, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 92%, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 101;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .boot-sequence { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .boot-line {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(0.4rem, 2.5vw, 0.55rem);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: bootIn 0.3s ease forwards;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  .b1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .b2 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .b3 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  @keyframes bootIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-4px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .logo-wrap { position: relative; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow: hidden; }
  .logo-art {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(7px, calc((100vw - 30px) / 38), 22px);
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--phosphor-glow), 0 0 24px rgba(200,255,0,0.12);
    white-space: pre;
    margin: 0;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    animation: logoIn 0.6s ease 1s both;
  }
  @keyframes logoIn {
    0% { opacity: 0; filter: brightness(4) blur(2px); }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; filter: brightness(1.8) blur(0.5px); }
    100% { opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1); }
  }
  .crt-scanline {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--phosphor);
    opacity: 0.06;
    animation: scanDrop 3s linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @keyframes scanDrop { 0% { top: 0; } 100% { top: 100%; } }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 4.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 1.4s both;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 1.6s both;
  }
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease 1.8s both;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--bg);
    background: var(--phosphor);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .btn-ghost {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--text-dim); color: var(--text); }

  /* MATRIX */
  .matrix-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .matrix-status {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--phosphor);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.5; } }

  .matrix-wrap {
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: matrixBreathe 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    will-change: box-shadow, border-color;
  }
  @keyframes matrixBreathe {
    0%,100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0px transparent, inset 0 0 0px transparent; border-color: var(--border); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(200,255,0,0.04), inset 0 0 20px rgba(200,255,0,0.02); border-color: rgba(200,255,0,0.15); }
  }
  #matrix-canvas {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    image-rendering: pixelated;
  }
  /* regime badge animations handled in canvas via opacity cycling */

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section { padding: 2.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.45rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3.5vw, 1.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ═══ PROPOSAL E: SCROLL REVEAL ═══ */
  .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .reveal-child { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: .1s; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: .2s; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: .3s; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: .4s; }
  .reveal.visible .reveal-child:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: .5s; }

  /* ═══ EDGE CONTRAST ═══ */
  .edge-contrast { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .edge-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,26,26,0.3);
  }
  .edge-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .edge-them {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: line-through;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .edge-us {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ═══ PROPOSAL A: REGIME VISUALIZER ═══ */
  .regime-viz { margin-top: 1rem; }
  .rv-bar-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .rv-bar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr 42px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
  }
  .rv-label { font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-align: right; }
  .rv-track {
    position: relative;
    height: 20px;
    background: rgba(26,26,26,0.6);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .rv-fill {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,255,0,0.15), rgba(200,255,0,0.05));
    transition: width 0.8s ease, background 0.8s ease;
  }
  .rv-fill-lyap {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.1), rgba(255,51,51,0.15));
  }
  .rv-marker {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2px; bottom: 2px;
    width: 3px;
    left: 50%;
    background: var(--phosphor);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--phosphor-glow);
    transition: left 0.8s ease, background 0.8s ease, box-shadow 0.8s ease;
    will-change: left;
  }
  .rv-val {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .rv-output {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .rv-regime-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
  }
  .rv-regime-badge.trending { color: var(--phosphor); border-color: var(--phosphor); background: rgba(200,255,0,0.08); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(200,255,0,0.1); }
  .rv-regime-badge.reverting { color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--amber); background: rgba(255,176,0,0.08); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,176,0,0.1); }
  .rv-regime-badge.chaotic { color: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); background: rgba(255,51,51,0.08); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,51,51,0.1); animation: chaosPulse 0.8s ease infinite; }
  .rv-regime-badge.shift { color: var(--ice); border-color: var(--ice); background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06); }
  @keyframes chaosPulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;}50%{opacity:.5;} }
  .rv-verdict {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
